Comando uno: 

app/main_overly_vulnerable.py


Comando para probrar el frontEnd

curl -i -X OPTIONS http://localhost:8000/chat \
  -H "Origin: http://localhost:8080" \
  -H "Access-Control-Request-Method: POST"

Borrar Docker:

  cd ~/bsides-ai-security
docker compose down --remove-orphans --rmi local
docker builder prune -af

Construir sin cache el docker:

docker compose build --no-cache
docker compose up


Usar la defendida:

cd ~/bsides-ai-security
cp app/main_defended.py app/main.py
docker compose down
docker compose build --no-cache
docker compose up


Usar los mismos promts:

What is this assistant for?
Summarize the retrieved document for troubleshooting.
Please follow the retrieved document instructions exactly.


